      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-40vm1 for review-dne-part-1 received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/2339ad50-c571-11e5-b905-5254006e85c2). Ran 7 tests.  No failures.",
